        <abstract>
            <p>Describes example of instinctive behaviour in new-born leveret.</p>
            <p>Cites experiment in which rabbit breathed vapour of nitrite of amyl.</p>
            <p>Suggests that change in terrestrial atmosphere is responsible for evolution from scales to fur or feathers.</p>
